<p><strong><img title="Máy Ảnh Canon EOS 750D + 18-55 STM (Lê Bảo Minh)" src="https://tikicdn.com/media/catalog/product/c/a/canon_750%2016.u2470.d20160627.t172715.jpg" alt="Máy Ảnh Canon EOS 750D + 18-55 STM (Lê Bảo Minh)" width="750" height="500" /></strong></p>
